
### OVERVIEW

App Name: SysAdmin
Version: 1.1
Author: Anjaneyulu Bollimuntha

Support Contact:anjirhl@gmail.com

Description of the App:

The Splunk Auditor app provides an unique view of key metrics and trends derived using splunk internal indexes (_internal,_audit) and rest URI inputs.

Prerequisites:

•	Splunk Enterprise / light / cloud server.
•	Log data with interal source types : _internal,_audit and |rest details.

### INSTALLATION

The SysAdmin app has been provided as a “.tar.gz” file. Please follow the below standard app import process in Splunk through “Manage Apps” menu to install the SysAdmin App.

Steps:

>> Click on the “Manage Apps” from Apps drop down and Choose “Install app from file” option.

>> Restart the splunk to load the app with custom visualizations.  


### USER GUIDE


Splunk Users and Activity:

Panels from this dashboard provide user specific information and trends like below.

    - Total Splunk Users.
    - Active Sessions - Now.
    - Splunk User Logon Trend - Daily.
    - Splunk Usesr Count - By Role.
    - Top 10 Usesr Count - Execution Time 
    - Top 10 Usesr Count - No Of Executions.
	- Top 10 Users - Non Of Searches Owned.
	- Top 10 Users - Disk Usage
	- Users Overview
Splunk Searches and Schedules:

This dashboard provides the information about he searches being executed and schduled in environments and top 10 metrics on usage.

	- Saved Searches
	- Scheduled Searches
	- Search - AVG Run Time
	- Search Activity - All Status
	- Scheduled Searches - By App
	- Search Activity - Completed
	- Top 10 Searches - ExecutionTime
	- Top 10 Searches - No of Runs

Splunk Infrastructure // knowledge Objects

This dashboard provides critical metric information about the splunk knowledge Objects and top usage trends. 

	- knowledge Object count(Hosts,Indexes,Sourcetypes,Custom Splunk Apps,saved searches,Dashboards,lookups,extractions and event-types)
	- Top 10 - Indexes
	- Top 10 - Sourcetypes
	- Dashboard Count By App
	- Lookup Count By App
	- Splunk Apps List


